#: ../../../release/dev/ctest-passthrough-args.rst:4
msgid ""
":manual:`ctest(1)` gained support for forwarding extra arguments to test "
"executables using a :option:`-- <ctest -->` separator."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/ctest-passthrough-args.rst:7
msgid ""
